comments: Tatum (BOS) touches the ball last before going out of bounds.
Holiday (MIL) places two hands on Smart (BOS) but the contact is marginal as he disengages during the throw-in.

Holiday (MIL) makes contact with Smart's (BOS) head as he makes a natural basketball move towards the basket.  Contact to an opponent?s head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
Horford (BOS) places an arm against Matthews (MIL) but the contact is marginal and does not affect his ability to get to the rebound.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) is in the lane for three seconds without actively guarding an opponent, but the shot is imminent.
Williams (BOS) initiates contact with Antetokounmpo (MIL) that causes the two players' arms to get tangled, but the contact does not affect Antetokounmpo's FOM or ability to control the rebound.
Horford (BOS) makes contact with Portis?s (MIL) back without extending or affecting his shot.
Portis (MIL) makes a field goal attempt that misses the backboard, rim or other player, and is the first to touch his own shot.
Portis (MIL) makes marginal contact with Horford's (BOS) arm as they mutually engage during the rebound.
Portis (MIL) reaches in and makes contact with Tatum's (BOS) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Williams (BOS) steps into Antetokounmpo's (MIL) path and initiates contact to his right arm and body that affects his SQBR.
Williams (BOS) makes contact to Antetokounmpo's (MIL) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Portis (MIL), Brown (BOS), and Smart (BOS) make incidental contact with each other during the rebound.
Connaughton (MIL) is in a legal guarding position as he moves alongside of Smart's (BOS) path to the basket and Holiday (MIL) makes clean contact with the ball to dislodge it.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) releases the throw-in within five seconds.
The ball is last touched by Smart (BOS) before going out of bounds.
White (BOS) commits a take foul on Connaughton (MIL).
Holiday (MIL) cleanly deflects the ball away from Smart (BOS) during the steal.
